{"tid":647481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏国崛起] 華為:可預見的未來 沒有發布自家操作系統計劃","createTime":"2018-04-30T01:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T05:50:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af32e158d50d8fe4b9c7038245d79cf927c11ef7","tid":647481,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:02:25.000Z","msg":"華為:可預見的未來 沒有發布自家操作系統計劃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1831265/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%3A%E5%8F%AF%E9%A0%90%E8%A6%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86+%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%B6%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F1831265%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%253A%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A6%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%2B%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2593%258D%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583&d=iasvbpCkUkVJl2lTLqQ2pP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ded3bde1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1831265/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%3A%E5%8F%AF%E9%A0%90%E8%A6%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86+%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%B6%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83</a><br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n《南華早報》最近報道，內地通訊解決方案供應商--華為，正在研發自家智能手機操作系統；其後，<span style=\"color: red;\">華為向內地《澎湃新聞》作出回應，表示在可預見的未來，華為沒有發布操作系統的計劃，重心在Android 操作系統的產品，公司對於移動操作系統持開放態度，會不斷努力通過持續創新、行業開放合作，為消費者提供優質的綜合體驗，並將致力於此。</span><br />\n<br />\n谷歌開發的Android系統，目前是全球最流行的開源操作系統，不過市場擔心，美國政府在處罰外國公司時，可以禁止外國公司使用該系統，因此系統的開放程度及安全性就受到影響。"},{"pid":"9125df0ebfb73f9a63e3bb4a37f01afacbeca3ba","tid":647481,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}